prelude on the babylonian captivity of t.data-term: prelude on the babylonian captivity of the church

examples.en: If you're superstitious, a black cat portends trouble.
The superstitious man is on the same plane as the savage.
I am extremely superstitious, and think his coming into it was of evil augury.
The superstitious terror with which that meteor-shower would have been regarded in old times.
He's very superstitious and won't pitch without his lucky mitt.
